burlap.behavior.functionapproximation.sparse

Class SparseCrossProductFeatures

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.functionapproximation.sparse.SparseCrossProductFeatures
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SparseStateActionFeatures

    public class SparseCrossProductFeatures
extends Object
implements SparseStateActionFeatures
    A SparseStateActionFeatures implementation that takes as input a SparseStateFeatures object, and turns it into state-action features taking the cross product of the features with the action set. This implementation is lazy and creates state-action features as they are queried. Consequently, the state-action feature indices for an action may not be consecutive.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan.
